10 SUMMARY
1151 This bill increases funding for the Bridging Rental Assistance Program to reduce the
1162 waiting list for assistance and increase housing vouchers by addressing the increase in
1173 program costs resulting from a 2021 policy change that increased the portion of a
1184 participant's rent paid by the program.
